user, and psst a bid to get someone's attention. Pfft is an expression 
of discontent, and brrr a way to say you are cold.

And euoi, a cry of Bacchic frenzy, is remembered by connosieurs using the phrase Excessive Units Of Intoxication.

Jiao, a monetary unit in Japan, is given the mnemonic: John Is Always Out.

